[section:has_next `has_next`]

[section Synopsis]
[reference__has_next]
[endsect]

[section Description]
This metafunction evaluates to __mpl_true__ if the specified type is defined
with a nested `next` type definition that is not `void`.  This metafunction
evaluates to __mpl_false__ otherwise.
[endsect]

[section:definition Where defined]
``
#include <__has_next__header__>
``

--or--

``
#include <__concept_traits__header__>
``

Forward declaration:

``
#include <__nested_type__header_fwd__>
``

--or--

``
#include <__concept_traits__header_fwd__>
``
[endsect]

[endsect] [/ has_next]

